Package net.doo.snap.process

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OcrPerformer
    Performs Ocr and return class OcrResult if license or feature not available result will contains empty data
    ProcessingInfoProvider
    Provides class Document and class Page that should be processed or are already processed.
    ProcessorMonitor<T>
    Reacts on T processing finished
    TextRecognition
    Text recognition API.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DocumentLockProvider
    Locks access to documents. Can be used to either prevent processing or disable UI for corresponding documents.
    DocumentProcessingResult
    Result of the document draft processing
    DocumentProcessor
    Saves pdf documents using class DocumentDraft source Call in a background thread only. Not thread safe
    DocumentProcessorMonitor
    Reacts on class Document processing finished
    DocumentProcessorProvider
    Provides class DocumentProcessor if SDK license is valid
    OcrResult
    Represents result of OCR-performing. Optionally contains sandwiched pdf file
    OcrResultBlock
    Part of the optical character recognitions result. Each block represents a text paragraph, a text line or a word and contains information about it, like the found text, the bounding box, where in the image the paragraph/line/word can be found, the confidence value and the type.
    PageProcessorMonitor
    Reacts on class Page processing finished
    TextRecognizer
    Performs text recognition.
